    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideally suited for a buyer looking for a project or parts car. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust along the door sills and several large dents on the hood and rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and the headliner is beginning to sag. Mechanically, the car starts but suffers from a rough idle and a noticeable transmission slip between gears; it will require professional attention before it can be considered a reliable daily driver. Sold strictly as-is.",
