      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014basically a time capsule that looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it runs like a dream. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out if you want to chat more about it or come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) in showroom condition. This example features the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine paired with a G96 6-speed manual transaxle. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed, including an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal (RMS). The chassis is tightened by the factory M030 Sport Suspension package, utilizing uprated Bilstein dampers and larger-diameter anti-roll bars for precise turn-in and minimal body roll. The Arctic Silver Metallic paint shows zero signs of oxidation or road rash, and the interior leather remains taut with no bolster wear. Mechanical integrity is confirmed by a clean DME over-rev report and consistent compression across all cylinders. This is a turn-key, purist-spec 911 for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Zero cosmetic flaws. Clean title. Full service records included.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of a 'time capsule.' Meticulously maintained and garage-kept since day one, the exterior retains its original deep luster with absolutely zero imperfections, chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state\u2014the premium leather is supple with no signs of wear, and every control still has that crisp, factory feel. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service record and a recent multi-point inspection. With exceptionally low mileage and a history of single-owner care, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. It comes complete with all original documentation, two keys, and a clean title. Truly a rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This specimen remains in pristine condition, showcasing an immaculate exterior finish and a meticulously preserved interior. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, mirroring its original factory specifications. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it truly shows\u2014it\u2019s in showroom condition and drives like an absolute dream! It\u2019s basically spotless inside and out, perfect for someone who wants that brand-new feel without the dealership headache. I've kept up with every little bit of maintenance, so it's totally ready for its next adventure. Drop me a message if you want to come see it in person; I\u2019d love to show you around your potential new ride!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-tier condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering a crisp 8,000 RPM redline through its six independent throttle bodies. The VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero paint correction required, while the interior showcases impeccable Nappa leather bolster integrity. Mechanically flawless with a documented service history, this M3 offers the purist driving experience with modern-classic reliability.",
